        <h1>Internal Auditor Unit</h1>
        
        <div class="pageDescription"><p>The Internal Auditor Unitwill contribute to the overall achievement of defence objectives by providing support to the Ministry’s senior management in controlling and managing&nbsp; subordinate departments and agencies. Another principal task of the Internal Auditor Unit is to assess whether the internal control arrangements are appropriate, adequate and effective, and whether the arrangements are being implemented as intended. The Internal Auditor Unit is also able to undertake the provision of consultancy and advice, participate in development work and assist departments in their own risk assessments. </p></div>        
